parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Tire Wear and Alignment Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature tire wear can lead to reduced traction, increased stopping distance, and increased risk of tire failure, which can cause accidents. Alignment issues can cause the vehicle to wander or drift, making it difficult to control, and can also lead to uneven tire wear.
symptoms: Uneven tire wear
tire cupping
vibration in the rear end of the vehicle
vehicle wanders to the left or right
alignment problems.
